nine, ten,

710
00:56:01,474 --> 00:56:04,477
eleven, twelve,

711
00:56:04,477 --> 00:56:09,482
thirteen, fourteen, fifteen,

712
00:56:09,482 --> 00:56:14,487
sixteen, seventeen, eighteen,

713
00:56:14,487 --> 00:56:19,993
nineteen and twenty.

714
00:56:25,999 --> 00:56:27,500
