in countless studies,

720
00:57:08,958 --> 00:57:11,961
or propped up in the log
basket like a rag doll.

721
00:57:11,961 --> 00:57:15,465
Which do you fancy--
early Agatha Christie or
vintage S.S. Van Dine ?

722
00:57:15,965 --> 00:57:20,470
