Perhaps, best of all,

724
00:57:23,473 --> 00:57:25,975
A real 1930s murder weapon,
the Mashie Niblick.

725
00:57:26,476 --> 00:57:27,977
I've got one in my golf bag.

726
00:57:52,010 --> 00:57:55,011
Dear old Mashie Niblick.

727
00:57:55,511 --> 00:58:00,516
